ML_Model = []
precision = []
recall = []
mAP = []

#function to call for storing the results
def storeResults(model, a,b,c):
    ML_Model.append(model)
    precision.append(round(a, 3))
    recall.append(round(b, 3))
    mAP.append(round(c, 3))
